OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob Piper
OL,5,FBob Piper, Age 98, Royal Signals
OL,7,FInterviewed 7 July 2023
OL,9,FJoining the Royal Sussex Regiment, his
OL,10,Fhome regiment, Bob Piper transferred
OL,11,Fto the Royal Signals and became a
OL,12,Fwireless operator.
OL,14,FHe went to Normandy seven days after
OL,15,Fthe invasion as part of an advance
OL,16,Fparty to set up communication links
OL,17,Ffor the 15th Scottish Infantry
OL,18,FDivision which he was attached to.
OL,20,FHe remembers training for a long time
OL,21,Fbeforehand.
