OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob Piper
OL,5,F"We didn't even know where we were
OL,6,Fgoing," he said.
OL,8,F"And we went down to West Grinstead
OL,9,Fand Monty (General Montgomery) came
OL,10,Fand did his thing and said 'You are
OL,11,Fgoing in.'
OL,13,F"And he shook hands with everybody and
OL,14,Fsaid 'Good luck and I hope I see you
OL,15,Fall when it's all over."
OL,17,FMr Piper said on D-Day itself the part
OL,18,Fof Sussex he was in got very busy
OL,19,Fbefore he left for his departure point
OL,20,Fof Southampton.
