OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob Piper
OL,5,F"Everywhere was stacked up with tanks,
OL,6,Florries and the woods were packed with
OL,7,Fstacks of petrol and ammunition dumps
OL,8,Fand on the road there was metal sheds
OL,9,Ffull of ammunition.
OL,11,F"Eventually they said you are ready to
OL,12,Fgo and the Americans were one side and
OL,13,Fwe were down the other.
OL,15,F"We had already waterproofed the
OL,16,Fvehicles and the wireless sets. We put
OL,17,Fa groundsheet up the front of the
OL,18,Fvehicle so when we hit the water it
OL,19,Fdidn't come in and smash the radiator."
