OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob Piper
OL,5,FOnce in France he operated from
OL,6,Ffoxholes dug in the ground and taught
OL,7,Fofficers how to use wireless sets.
OL,9,F"All the time you were either digging
OL,10,Fa hole in the ground or there with the
OL,11,Fheadphones on. We were reasonably safe
OL,12,Falthough we lost a wireless truck and
OL,13,Fa (Messerschmitt) 109 came over and
OL,14,Fshot it up and the signal office
OL,15,Fcaught fire.
